helpMessage:
Type /help or ?help command to get info about the commands and how to use them. 
 Commands: 
 /timer /rules /help /cancel /end /say /w // 
 ?timer ?rules ?help ?cancel ?end ?say ?w ??
rulesMessage: Rules will be updated into the Game soon.
timerMessage: type /timer or ?timer to see the timer during a match.
AnnouncementMessage: Please ensure all Players are Linked to AutoMuteUs and that the match is started.
wrongCommandMessage: Wrong Command, please use one of the following commands: /timer | /help | /rules | /say
cancelMessage: The host of the game can cancel a match at any point with the /cancel or ?cancel command followed up by a /end or ?end
impChatMessage:
Use any of the following to use the ImpostorChat, Your partners message will display in Red. 
 Prefixes: // ?? /w ?w /say ?say 
 Examples: 
 /say message 
 //message 
 ?say message 
 ??message 
 /w message 
 ?w message
